I asked Arteta about Ceballos this week and whether he sees him as a major part of his plans given he is heading back to Madrid in the summer:<br />
<br />
&quot;He is a player that can fit our style and now he needs to make a step forward and make things difficult for me and my selection.&quot;

Matteo was really good when he came on as well, but Lucas has been in good form,&quot; our head coach said. &quot;He's given us a lot but I had to get him off because he wasn't feeling good.<br />
<br />
&quot;It's a muscle injury. We'll have to assess it with the doctors tomorrow. We will know more the day after.&quot;

